"      Patient information: Insect bites and stings (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/35/17971?source=related_link\">",
"      Patient information: Peanut allergy (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"UTD.htm?27/30/28134?source=related_link\">",
